    "With constant vigilance and proper adaptation into the corresponding ethical and legal framework, these measures, such as the establishment of regulatory agencies dedicated to medical AI, increased awareness of data privacy, and the demand for traceability and explainability as prerequisites for the certification of AI systems [3], could also be applicable for a safer use of ChatGPT.While the use of AI in healthcare creates the need for stronger, transparent, and unbiased policy initiatives and regulatory interventions, the use of ChatGPT has contributed to the push for that need.",
